		"reviewID": 196271,
		"rating": 5,
		"text": "My boyfriend LOVES this recipe.  If the sauce is too greasy, I put the sauce in a container in the freezer while I'm shredding the beef.  The grease hardens on top, and you can skim it off.  Then you can return it to the slow cooker with the shredded beef.  Excellent!!!",
